    • getImageSourceURI

      @Nullable String getImageSourceURI(Element e)
      For an element where isImageElement returns true, retrieves the URI associated with that Image, as reported by the element; makes no guarantee that the URI is correct, complete or points to anything in particular. For elements where isImageElement(Element) returns false, this method may return false, and may also return false if the Element is not correctly formed and contains no URI; check the return value carefully.
      Parameters:
      e - The element to extract image info from.
      Returns:
      String containing the URI for the image.
